2. DSPy (Stanford NLP / dspy-ai) — optional dependency
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Source:  https://github.com/stanfordnlp/dspy
License: MIT
PyPI:    https://pypi.org/project/dspy-ai/

DSPy is an optional extra dependency used for structured prompt optimization.
It is NOT baked into the base OS image; it is available as an installable
extra for downstream consumers of hermes-runtime:

  pip install "hermes-runtime[dspy]"

See https://github.com/stanfordnlp/dspy/blob/main/LICENSE for the full MIT
license text.

